::GoldenEye/KitKat::

GoldenEye  took a shot tot he chest and doubled over in pain.  She 
rose and returned fire on Stronghold and Doom Ice.



KitKat  redeived several shots to the shoulder and chest.  She fell 
down and layed on the ground near the entrance of the cave.  She 
called to the computer,"OPEN FIRE IN MAXIMAL SIGNATURES!" She layed 
there breathing hard and trying to catch her breath.  She wondered 
why she always got so darned beat up in battle.  She thought thaqt 
one of these days, those maximals would get lucky and get her foe 
good.  But not today.  She rose to her knees and returned fire.

The computer opened autogun fire on Deemos, Doom Ice, StrongHold, 
Razopas, and all the other Maximals.
